{"ID":"20250708131530-si2w3ba","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20250708131530-si2w3ba","title":"待办","type":"doc","updated":"20260317132836"},"Children":[{"ID":"20251103141927-wyc4t1t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251103141927-wyc4t1t","updated":"20251103141927"}},{"ID":"20251124110114-12texqk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251124110114-12texqk","updated":"20251124110419"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海外EP2的车子赶紧还掉，包括海外，海外车辆控制目标4台以内，春节前"}]},{"ID":"20251124110250-oklgyiv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251124110250-oklgyiv","updated":"20251124110516"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"DM1 武汉的P车还掉，小红给武汉，大红留着；海波的车子1215基线发完后还掉"}]},{"ID":"20251124110549-pxd7tv2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251124110549-pxd7tv2","updated":"20251124110829"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"CG carplay认证的车子还掉；武汉的三台PP车，还掉一台T1的PP车；SSV164还掉；9470保养保养；SSV004武汉的P车拉回来还掉"}]},{"ID":"20251124110900-0t390kb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251124110900-0t390kb","updated":"20251124110953"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"8155 陈明瀚的车子，今年年底基线发完后还掉；8155整体就留1台车；费用化完成后的车子可以不用还"}]},{"ID":"20251125134924-bictxnr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251125134924-bictxnr","updated":"20251208181333"}},{"ID":"20260317131941-d8h4fbf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260317131941-d8h4fbf","updated":"20260317131941"}},{"ID":"20260316142243-ogtcpxd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260316142243-ogtcpxd","updated":"20260316142243"}}]}